TRUENOISE — SYSTEM DOCUMENTATION
=================================
Generated May 2026
For: Marty Krizan, truenoise.org

This document describes every system, service, and file that makes up the
TrueNoise platform. It is written for someone who understands the project
but may not remember every technical detail six months from now.

