7. UPTIMEROBOT (uptimerobot.com)
─────────────────────────────────
Role: Uptime monitor — pings the Render API every 5 minutes to prevent
it from sleeping.

Render's free tier spins down web services after 15 minutes of inactivity.
The first request after a spin-down takes up to 50 seconds. UptimeRobot
solves this by sending a GET request to the /health endpoint every 5 minutes,
keeping Render awake continuously.

UptimeRobot also serves as an alert system — if the Render service goes
down unexpectedly, UptimeRobot will send an email notification.

Monitor URL: https://aircraft-noise-tracker-api.onrender.com/health
Check interval: every 5 minutes
Plan: Free tier


